      "historical_median_m3s": 85,
      "description": "The Shabelle River at Beledweyne is Somalia's most flood-prone point. The November 2023 floods displaced over 500,000 people. The river receives upstream rainfall from the Ethiopian highlands."
    },
    {
      "id": "juba",
